d Class of 1978   Ivan A  Moore  Jr  Class of 1979   Nicholas C  Kepf Class of 1980   Robert B  Gore Class of 1981   Jeffrey M  Gill Class of 1982   Gordon R  Hammock Class of 1983   John C  Manning Class of 1984   Ralph A  Foertsch Class of 1985   Daniel W  Murphy Class of 1986   Joseph J  Thompson  III Class of 1987   Kevin P  Sincavage Class of 1988   Trent H  Beck Class of 1989   Thomas D  Shelton Class of 1990   John B  Cabell Class of 1991   Kyle A  Bryan Class of 1992   David F  Brugger Class of 1993   Troy D  Spencer Class of 1994   Nicolas B  Schweizer Class of 1995   Jeremy Ingram Class of 1996   John D  Adams Class of 1997   David O  Cooper Class of 1998   Michael P  Harris Class of 1999   Micheal J  Rust Class of 2000   Michael P  Goldman Class of 2001   Sean J  Collins Class of 2002   Peter Sok Class of 2003   Jordan E  Fox Class of 2004   Brandon M  Smith Class of 2005   William K  DeShazor Class of 2006   Bradley B  Bascope Class of 2006   Tadas Mandevicius Class of 2007   Richard Meredith Class of 2008   Garrett R  Smith Class of 2009  Daniel C  Allen Class of 2010   Daniel L  Welsh Class of 2011   Nathanael R  Salatin Class of 2012   Michael W  Bowman Class of 2013   William D  Alewine Class of 2014   William M  Breakell   The Philpott Medal  Established in honor of John Robert Philpott  Class of 1935  to acknowledge his efforts as National Chairman of the Economics Fund Drive  which resulted in the establishment of the Mary Moody Northen Chair in the Arts and Social Sciences  Until the spring of 2008  the medal recognized excellence in business studies by an Economics and Business major in the graduating class  Currently  the medal recognizes outstanding performance in research by an economics and business major in the graduating class  Class of 1987   Ronald A  Robinson  Jr  Class of 1988   Trent H  Beck Class of 1989   Thomas D  Shelton Class of 1990   Robert J  Uhorchuk  II Class of 1991   David K  Raucher Class fo 1992   Mark C  Thackston Class